---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`Cookies 2026 - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Cookie sale information and resources for 2026" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="cookies-content">
				<h1>Girl Scout Cookies 2026</h1>

				<section class="links-section">
					<ul>
						<li>Preorders are open for cookie delivery mid-Feburary!</li>
						<li><a href="https://digitalcookie.girlscouts.org/scout/winifred83871" class="order-link">Click here</a> to order your Girl Scout Cookies!</li>
						<li>Or let us know if you'd like to order your cookies in person.</li>
					</ul>
				</section>
				<p class="intro">
				</p>
				<!--
				<p class="intro">
				Cookies are $6/box. Our troop earns at least $1/box that our girls sell. This money is pooled within the troop and pays for most of our troop activities throughout the year, allowing the girls to plan activities within the troop's budget, not the budget of individual scouts. Most of the rest of the cookie cost goes to the local/regional GS organization to support affordable programs in STEM, outdoors, and life skills (which our girls participate in). 5% goes to individual girl prizes and badges. 20% of the cookie cost goes to the bakery.
				</p>
				-->



				<section class="media-section">
					<h2>Photos & Videos</h2>
					<div class="media-grid">
						<!-- Add your photos and videos here -->
						<div class="media-placeholder">
						<iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cH6llpB7tFA?si=zwoD12oM-fgX7Q3u" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
<style>
	.cookies-content {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2rem;
		font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
	}

	h1 {
		font-family: 'Palatino Linotype', Palatino, serif;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: bold;
		margin: 0 -2rem 1.5rem -2rem;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		background: #005640;
		color: white;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.intro {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	section {
		margin: 3rem 0;
	}

	h2 {
		font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: bold;
		margin: 0 -2rem 1.5rem -2rem;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		background: #622e8b;
		color: white;
		border-radius: 8px;
	}

	.links-section ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.links-section li {
		padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
		background: white;
		border: 3px solid var(--star-green);
		border-radius: 15px;
		box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(var(--black), 5%);
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 600px;
		width: 100%;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--forest-green);
	}

	.links-section a.order-link {
		color: #622e8b;
		text-decoration: underline;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.links-section a.order-link:hover {
		color: #7a3aa3;
	}

	.media-grid {
		width: 100%;
	}

	.media-placeholder {
		position: relative;
		width: 100%;
		padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
		height: 0;
		overflow: hidden;
		border-radius: 10px;
	}

	.media-placeholder iframe {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		border: none;
	}
</style>
